reviewText: This is a great animation story depicting friendship, loyalty, working as a team and achieving goals. Good role model for my granddaughter.

Hope this review is helpful if you would like to purchase some Winx club dvds!!!

This set wraps up season two of the Winx Club (the 4Kids dub

So if you've made it this far, you know that this dub is the 4Kids Dub.
Also known as the dub with good voice acting yet has deviations from the plot, dialogues, and missing scenes pretty much every episode. While there are changes from the original work. The Dub still does a fantastic job of capturing the essence of Winx Club and still is a lot of fun to watch, especially for the kids. To get the complete Winx experience, you have to watch this 4Kids Dub, The Rai dub, Nickelodeon dub, and the Duarts season 7. With that said, bear in mind that no matter which dub you choose, you may have to switch over to finish the series, since no dub has been able to complete the entire series from beginning to end. While that can be distracting to hear all your favorite characters voices change. This 4Kids Dubs is a good place to start, along with the Rai Dub.
